This cauliflower and caramelised onion lasagna is the perfect super cheesy vegetarian recipe to recreate as a midweek meal.  This lasagna recipe feeds 8, and can be served alongside your favourite fresh salad. Substitute all the diary products with vegan products to make this a delicious dairy-free and vegan lasagna which you and your family will be sure to love.  ALSO TRY: 5 delicious and hearty recipes to recreate using mixed vegetables This recipe was found on taste.com.au